  - `Event` struct + setters + JSON/text formatting
  - `EventEmitter` format selection
  - Extensive tests
- But there were no runtime emission sites; `Event::new()` calls were mostly tests.
- `cli::RunArgs` originally had no `--log-format` field.
- Existing runtime paths:
  - `main.rs::cmd_run` executes mint, runs child, handles signal forwarding, and revocation
  - `orchestrator::mint_all` is central mint fanout path
  - `refresh::RefreshRuntimeLoop::run_once` is refresh execution path
  - `main.rs::execute_revoke` and `integration_runtime::revoke_token` are revoke paths
  - `agent_process.rs` handles spawn/wait
